Deleted Tag: <script>
		function whenAvailable(name, callback) {
			var interval = 10; //ms
			window.setTimeout(function () {
				if (window[name]) {
					callback(window[name]);
				} else {
					window.setTimeout(arguments.callee, interval);
				}
			}, interval);
		}

		// Create or remove dyid_server cookie based on OneTrust consent.
		function createDyidServerCookie(consented) {
			var _dyid_cookie = "_dyid";
			var _dyid_server_cookie = "_dyid_server";

			var cookies_array = document.cookie.split(';');

			function getCookieValue(cookie_name, cookies_array) {
				if (cookies_array) {
					for (var i = 0; i < cookies_array.length; i++) {
						var cookie = cookies_array[i].trim();
						if (cookie.indexOf(cookie_name + '=') == 0) {
							return cookie.substring(_dyid_cookie.length + 1, cookie.length);
						}
					}
				}
				return "";
			}

			var _dyid_value = getCookieValue(_dyid_cookie, cookies_array);

			if (_dyid_value != "" && getCookieValue(_dyid_server_cookie, cookies_array) == "") {
				var expiry_date = new Date();
				expiry_date.setTime(expiry_date.getTime() + (365 * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
				document.cookie = _dyid_server_cookie + "=" + _dyid_value + ";expires=" + expiry_date.toUTCString() +
					";secure;path=/";
			}

			if (!consented) {
				document.cookie = _dyid_server_cookie + "=; expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 UTC; path=/";
			}
		}

		// Update the status of Dynamic Yield consent.
		function updateDYTracking(consented) {
			console.log('Setting DY Consent to:', consented);
			DY.userActiveConsent = {
				accepted: consented
			};
			DYO.ActiveConsent.updateConsentAcceptedStatus(consented);

			// Create or remove dyid_server cookie based on the consent.
			createDyidServerCookie(consented);
		}

		// Check OneTrust Consent.
		function checkOneTrustSettings() {
			whenAvailable('OneTrust', function () {
				whenAvailable('OnetrustActiveGroups', function () {
					cookie = OneTrust.GetDomainData().Groups.find((current) => current.CustomGroupId ==
						"C073");
					if (cookie) {
						// If the cookie is present, check if CustomGroupId is among OnetrustActiveGroups
						// and set DY consent.
						updateDYTracking(OnetrustActiveGroups.includes(cookie.CustomGroupId));
					}
				});
			});
		}

		// Tracking changes to the OneTrust consent.
		function onOneTrustConsentChange(event) {
			checkOneTrustSettings();
		}

		// Set DY consent according to OneTrust settings.
		if (DY) {
			checkOneTrustSettings();
		}

		// When OneTrust consent changes, update DY consent.
		window.addEventListener('consent.onetrust', onOneTrustConsentChange);

		// When page reloads, dyid_server cookie to be created after dyid is created
		function createDyidServerCookieOnLoad(event) {
			createDyidServerCookie(true);
		}

		window.addEventListener('load', createDyidServerCookieOnLoad);
	</script>

				ogUrl.setAttribute("content", window.location.href);
			}

			var ogImage = document.body.querySelector('meta[property="og:image"]');
			if (ogImage) {
